profile:
SHOULD'A GOT US is a new company by name only.
However, the company has well over 15 years of experience and knowledge.
 
SHOULD’A GOT US was aptly named by our own clients and their neighbours who would stop by at various job sites and compliment us about our workmanship. Then, they would comment on their own past work experiences with which they were not completely satisfied.  In response, we simply said: You SHOULD’A GOT US!
 
We at SHOULD'A GOT US, take great pride in our work from the beginning of each and every project from start to finish and we strive to complete the jobs on time and when possible below budget.

 
Please take the time to research our work, look at our gallery of photos, and to read the comments of our satisfied clients.
 
References will gladly be furnished on request.
 

Thank you, 
Larry Rudd

First Class Craftmanship

That's how we describe our bussiness. We provide residential and commercial clients throughout the Simcoe/Grey and surrounding areas with fast and reliable home repairs.

WE ARE PASSIONATE

We are a professional, safe, reliable handyman service for your entire To Do list .

HONEST AND DEPENDABLE

That's why local residents choose our professional handyman service. We specialize in ALL major and minor home repairs.

CALL US TODAY - (705) 445-1497 - WE ARE AVAILABLE 24/7/365

Call or email, we are ready to fix your home repair issues. If you need to leave a message we will contact you within 24 hours.
